# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI Agent — Files to exclude from version control
# Merge these entries into your project's .gitignore
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Agent memory — machine/session-specific, grows over time
.opencode/memory/episodic/sessions.md
.opencode/memory/prospective/goals.md
.opencode/memory/retrieval/codebase_index.md
.opencode/memory/semantic/user_preferences.md

# Document ingestion — raw input files (often large binaries)
docs/input/
docs/parsed/

# Python cache from doc_watcher
scripts/__pycache__/
*.pyc
